additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Hazard Classifications 9.1D, 6.3B Read label before use Causes mild skin irritation If skin irritation occurs: Get medical advice/ attention Toxic to aquatic life. This substance must not be applied into or onto water. DO NOT place baits in areas accessible to children or pets. DO NOT spray insecticide on or around the baits as sprays will contaminate baits and reduce effectiveness. DO NOT allow the bait to contact food, food preparation areas or food utensils. DO NOT allow chemical containers or spray to get into drains, sewers, streams or ponds.
